                                    <li>Contact us via the contact us form or send an email to <b>sales@antelecom.net.</b> Don't forget to check your details. If you make a mistake we might not be able to contact you!</li>
                                    <li> Once we've answered your initial questions. Our sales engineers will confirm service availability and arrange a site survey if necessary.</li>
